  <md:abstract>By the end of this section, you will be able to:
<list>
<item>Discuss how human population growth can be exponential</item>
<item>Explain how humans have expanded the carrying capacity of their habitat</item>
<item>Relate population growth and age structure to the level of economic development in different countries</item>
<item>Discuss the long-term implications of unchecked human population growth</item>
