<section id="fs-idm322306688" class="summary">
<title>Section Summary</title><para id="fs-idm48316864">The world’s human population is growing at an exponential rate. Humans have increased the world’s carrying capacity through migration, agriculture, medical advances, and communication. The age structure of a population allows us to predict population growth. Unchecked human population growth could have dire long-term effects on our environment.</para>
</section>
